# tomcat

$ copy-file sbt/tomcat.sbt tomcat.sbt

## basic tomcat

> reload
> tomcat:start
> await 8080
> get http://localhost:8080/test 200
> tomcat:stop
-> get http://localhost:8080/test 200

## jetty

$ delete tomcat.sbt
$ copy-file sbt/jetty.sbt jetty.sbt

## basic jetty

> reload
> jetty:start
> await 8080
> get http://localhost:8080/test 200
> jetty:stop
-> get http://localhost:8080/test 200

## jetty with jetty.xml

> reload
> 'set containerArgs := Seq("--config", s"${baseDirectory.value}/etc/jetty.xml")'
> jetty:start
> await 8080
> await 8443
> get http://localhost:8080/test 200
> get https://localhost:8443/test 200
> jetty:stop
-> get http://localhost:8080/test 200
-> get https://localhost:8443/test 200
